div.pre:
. As a user, I want the system to load all my inputs from a font, so I can later process them from the system
- As a user, i want the system to allow me to relation inputs with one or more objectives, so they can inherite it importance value
. As a user, I want the system to allow me to modify a loaded Input content, so I can process it in a better way
. As a user, I want that, when I want to clarify my most important loaded Inputs, the system let me do it Input by Input, so I can clarify in a orderly way
. As a user, I want that, when I finish to clarify a set of Inputs, the system leaves them available to be organized, so I can advance in this process
. As a user, I want that, if I loaded an Input and then I want to quit it from the clarification, the system removes that input from the process, so I'm able to clarify only what I want
